Applying for a bakery account is quick and easy!

### 1. Make sure you fit all of the requirements

- Be based in the United States
- Have a bank account
- Have verifiable baking or decorating experience
- Completed all the registrations and obtained the licenses and permits required in your local jurisdiction.

### 2. Overview of opening a Frosting Shop

Check out [How do I open a Frosting Shop](https://frosting.helpscoutdocs.com/article/68-how-do-i-open-a-frosting-shop) for an overview of the process.

### 3.  Apply

Apply in minutes using our [Bakery Application](https://bakeryapplication.paperform.co/?utm_source=helpdocs&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=hsd)
